{"tid":380632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［想搵支結他］ 回憶係哂入面","createTime":"2017-08-30T09:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T23:04:22.000Z","uid":15569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"077120dc58b8322cfb097f42834ab40053db42ab","tid":380632,"uid":15569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲我想搵一支十年前出廠既結他<br />\n佢比人擅自拎走整爛然後揼左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢性能只係下游<br />\n但係佢有好多我同女朋友既回憶係哂入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我連淘寶都搵埋但係都沒消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為實在停左產太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然機會渺茫但我相信世界有奇蹟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/170440_5cd6832db62c008df5c11e2430ce84be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F170440_5cd6832db62c008df5c11e2430ce84be.jpg&h=93842fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牌子型號：starsun(星晨）CAG230C 藍色缺角（如圖）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重酬！有既巴絲可唔可以轉讓比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTelegram:wucfuuu"},{"pid":"1fe9816c5901692a5a12001f389ac170fcdd15c0","tid":380632,"uid":15569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:08:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"57a93a9d1e888f84319cb7ca223b853da9395d75","tid":380632,"uid":15569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:32:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ff1c42d726905c929d3c8bd536f3e7e1c7ae6c39","tid":380632,"uid":7090,"like"